on}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|title = \u56fd\u5185\u9996\u4efd\u539f\u521b\u6587\u5b66\u98ce\u4e91\u699c\u53d1\u5e03 \u9605\u6587\u96c6\u56e2\u6253\u9020IP\u4ea7\u4e1a\"\u5965\u65af\u5361\" - \u751f\u6d3b - \u91cd\u5e86\u5546\u62a5|url = http://www.chinacqsb.com/xw/sh/2016/01/062903.html|website = www.chinacqsb.com|accessdate = 2016-01-07|date = January 6, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[Sina Weibo|Weibo]] Night Awards Ceremony\n|Most Powerful Actor of the Year\n|Jin Dong\n|{{won}}\n|rowspan=\"7\"|<ref>{{Cite web|title = \u5434\u4ea6\u51e1\u8d75\u4e3d\u9896\u5206\u83b7\u5fae\u535a\u4e4b\u591cKing&Queen \u674e\u5149\u6d19-\u5b8b\u667a\u5b5d-Gary\u4e5f\u7eb7\u7eb7\u83b7\u5956 - \u5185\u5730\u660e\u661f\u516b\u5366 - \u5a31\u4e50\u65b0\u95fb - \u4e2d\u56fd\u5a31\u4e50\u7f51|url = http://news.yule.com.cn/html/201601/212707.html|website = news.yule.com.cn|accessdate = 2016-01-08|date = January 8, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|Most Powerful Actress of the Year\n|Liu Tao\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Newcomer of the Year\n|Leo Wu \n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Man of the Year\n|Wang Kai\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Performance by an Actress\n|Liu Min Tao\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Performance by an Actor\n|[[Liu Yijun (actor)|Liu Yijun]] \n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Television Series Producer\n|Hou Hongliang\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[State Administration of Press, Publication, Radio, Film and Television]]\n| Top 20 Most Outstanding Dramas of 2015\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''Nirvana in Fire''\n|{{won}}\n| \n|- \n| rowspan=\"9\" |1st China Quality Television Drama Ceremony\n|Quality Grand Award\n|{{won}}\n| rowspan=\"9\" |<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://he.people.com.cn/n2/2016/0310/c192235-27905458.html|title=\u4e2d\u56fd\u7535\u89c6\u5267\u54c1\u8d28\u76db\u5178 \u80e1\u6b4c\u970d\u5efa\u534e\"\u4ea4\u676f\"\u5e86\u83b7\u5956--\u6cb3\u5317\u9891\u9053--\u4eba\u6c11\u7f51|last=L_104350|date=March 10, 2016|website=[[People's Daily]]|access-date=2016-03-11}}</ref>\n|-\n|Audience Favorite TV Series ([[Dragon Television|Dragon TV]])\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Quality