{"title_page": "List of African films of 2014", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n<!-- Commented out: [[File:African Union flag.svg|thumb|right|200px]] -->\nThe film industries of the 54 countries that make up [[Africa]] produced over two hundred feature films in [[2014 in film|2014]]. This article fully lists all non-pornographic films, including short films, that had a release date in that year and which were at least partly made by an [[List of sovereign states and dependent territories in Africa|African country]]. It does not include films first released in previous years that had release dates in 2014. Nor does it include films made in countries such as [[France]], [[Spain]] or the [[United Kingdom]], which though they have territories in Africa are primarily non-African states, unless they are co-productions with African countries. <br> Also included is an overview of the major events in African film, including film festivals and awards ceremonies, as well as lists of those films that have been particularly well received, both critically and financially. The year was particularly notable for the release of ''[[Timbuktu (2014 film)|Timbuktu]]'', the first [[Mauritania]]n film ever nominated for the Academy Award for best foreign language film.\n\n==Major Releases==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ \"align=bottom\" |\n|- style=\"background:#b0e0e6; text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"2\" | Opening\n! style=\"width:20%;\"| Title\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Cast and Crew\n! Details\n! style=\"width:12%;\"| Country\n! style=\"width:8%;\"| Genre(s)\n! style=\"width:2%;\"| Ref.\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffa07a; textcolor:#000;\"|J<br>A<br>N<br>U<br>A<br>R<br>Y\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffdacc;\"| 17\n|''[[Fishing Without Nets (2014 film)|Fishing Without Nets]]''\n|| Director: [[Cutter Hodierne]] <br> Cast: Eric Godon, Abdiwali Farrah, Abdikhadir Hassan, [[Idil Ibrahim]], Abdi Kani, [[Reda Kateb]]\n|| Think Media Studios\n|| {{flag|Kenya}} <br> {{flag|Somalia}}\n|| [[Drama]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Fishing Without Nets|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fishing_without_nets_2013/?search=Fishing%20Without%20Nets|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=12 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffdacc;\"| 18\n|''[[Difret]]''\n|| Director: Zeresenay Berhane Mehari <br> Cast: Meron Getnet, Tizita Hagere\n|| Haile Addis Pictures\n|| {{flag|Ethiopia}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Difret|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/difret-2014|publisher=BBFC|accessdate=12 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Young Ones (film)|Bad Land: Road to Fury]]''\n|| Director: [[Jake Paltrow]] <br> Cast: [[Nicholas Hoult]], [[Elle Fanning]], [[Michael Shannon]], [[Kodi Smit-McPhee]]\n|| [[Screen Media Films]]\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Action film|Action]] <br> [[Science fiction film|Science Fiction]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=BAD LAND: ROAD TO FURY|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/bad-land-road-fury-2014|publisher=BBFC|accessdate=12 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; background:thistle; textcolor:#000;\"|F<br>E<br>B<br>R<br>U<br>A<br>R<br>Y\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#d8d8d8;\"| 7\n|''[[Two Men in Town (2014 film)|Two Men in Town]]''\n|| Director: [[Rachid Bouchareb]] <br> Cast: [[Forest Whitaker]], [[Harvey Keitel]], [[Ellen Burstyn]], [[Luis Guzm\u00e1n]], [[Brenda Blethyn]]\n|| Artists & Co <br> Remake of ''[[Two Men in Town (1973 film)|Deux hommes dans la ville]]'' ([[1973 in film|1973]])\n|| {{flag|Algeria}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Two Men in Town|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/two-men-town-2014|publisher=BBFC|accessdate=12 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background: