 film|Crime]] <br> [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Omoni Oboli, others break barrier with Render to Caesar|url=http://dailyindependentnig.com/2013/02/09/omoni-oboli-others-break-barrier-with-render-to-caesar/|publisher=Daily Independent|accessdate=12 December 2015}}{{Dead link|date=February 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffa07a; textcolor:#000;\"|A<br />P<br />R<br />I<br />L\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffdacc;\"| 4\n|''[[Island of Lemurs: Madagascar]]''\n|| Director: [[David Douglas (director)|David Douglas]] <br> Cast: [[Morgan Freeman]]\n|| [[Warner Bros.]]\n|| {{flag|Madagascar}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Island of Lemurs: Madagascar|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/island-lemurs-madagascar-2014|publisher=BBFC|accessdate=15 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffdacc;\"| 17\n|''[[Virunga (film)|Virunga]]''\n|| Director: [[Orlando von Einsiedel]]\n|| [[Netflix]]\n|| {{flag|Congo}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Virunga|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/virunga-2014|publisher=BBFC|accessdate=13 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffdacc;\"| 18\n|''[[Knocking on Heaven's Door (2014 film)|Knocking on Heaven's Door]]''\n|| Director: [[Desmond Elliot]] <br> Cast: [[Ini Edo]], Emem Isong\n|| Royal Arts Academy\n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Musical film|Musical]] <br> [[Romance film|Romance]] <br> [[Drama film|Drama]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Ini Edo, Majid Michel & Blossom Chukwujekwu Show Off Singing Chops in \"Knocking on Heaven\u2019s Doors\"|url=http://www.bellanaija.com/2014/03/19/ini-edo-majid-michel-blossom-chukwujekwu-show-off-singing-chops-in-knocking-on-he