ica}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Secret Act''\n|| Nonso Emekaekwue\n|| 1 April 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|-\n|''Secret Weapon''\n|| Nonso Emekaekwue\n|| 1 April 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|-\n|''Seun: Son''\n|| Darrell Roodt\n|| 1 December 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n|-\n|''Sexy Money''\n|| Karin Junger\n|| 3 April 2014 (Netherlands)\n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Shadow & Light''\n|| Hakim Ben Aissia\n|| 17 March 2014 (Tunisia)\n|| {{flag|Tunisia}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Shield and Spear''\n|| Petter Ringbom\n|| 12 June 2014 (UK)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Shower of Love''\n|| Matthew F. Smith\n|| \n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Sigauque''\n|| Abu Gudo\n|| 17 December 2014 (Mozambique)\n|| {{flag|Mozambique}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Sightlines''\n|| Genevieve Bicknell\n|| June 2014 (UK)\n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Simha''\n|| Jerome Blumberg\n|| \n|| {{flag|Central African Republic}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Simo Gabid: Are You Ready?''\n|| Lars Sundgot Slagsvold\n|| \n|| {{flag|Morocco}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Six Lives: A Cinepoem''\n|| Sarah Riggs\n|| \n|| {{flag|Morocco}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Slum Dreams''\n|| Brendan Modini\n|| \n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Soft Vengeance: Albie Sachs and the New South Africa''\n|| Abby Ginzberg\n|| 18 September 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Softwaring Hard''\n|| Alex Pop\n|| 31 October 2014 (Canada)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}} <br> {{flag|Uganda}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Sone'a Fee Misr''\n|| Amr Salama\n|| 28 July 2014 (Egypt)\n