14,2014|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=23 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Critical reception==\n\n===Metacritic===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"70%\" style=\"text-align:center; margin: 1em auto 1em auto;\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"5\"\n|+ Top 10 Best Reviewed Films (Critics)\n! width=5% | Rank\n! width=14% | Film\n! width=5% | Rating\n! width=5% | No. of reviews\n! style=\"width:1%;\"| Ref.\n|-\n| 1\n| ''[[Virunga (film)|Virunga]]''\n| 95%\n| 5\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Virunga|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/virunga|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2\n| ''[[Timbuktu (2014 film)|Timbuktu]]''\n| 92%\n| 30\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Timbuktu|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/timbuktu|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 3\n| ''[[Vessel (film)|Vessel]]''\n| 68%\n| 4\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Vessel|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/vessel|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 4\n| ''[[Island of Lemurs: Madagascar]]''\n| 66%\n| 12\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Island of Lemurs: Madagascar|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/island-of-lemurs-madagascar|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5\n| ''[[The Good Lie]]''\n| 65%\n| 30\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=The Good Lie|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-good-lie|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 6\n| ''[[Fishing Without Nets (2014 film)|Fishing Without Nets]]''\n| 65%\n| 9\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Fishing Without Nets|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fishing-without-nets|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=29 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===IMDb===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"70%\" style=\"text-align:center; margin: 1em auto 1em auto;\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"5\