: Ithala''\n|| Zuko Nodada\n|| July 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Comedy film|Comedy]]\n|-\n|''Between the Devil and the Deep''\n|| Heinrich Dahms\n|| \n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Beyond the Walls''\n|| Gayle Embrey\n|| \n|| {{flag|Liberia}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Big Dream''\n|| Kelly Cox\n|| \n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Blessing''\n|| Connor Clerke\n|| \n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Bloody Ring''\n|| Iyke Odife\n|| 1 April 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n|-\n|''Blood Rivals Lion vs Buffalo: Buffalo Fortress''\n|| Graeme Duane\n|| 30 September 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Bordering on Bad Behavior''\n|| Jac Mulder\n|| July 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Action film|Action]]\n|-\n|''Born to Win''\n|| [[Frans Cronje|Frans Cronj\u00e9]]\n|| 15 August 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n|-\n|''Boulanoir''\n|| Hamid Zoughi\n|| 8 October 2014 (Morocco)\n|| {{flag|Morocco}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n|-\n|''Boyhood''\n|| Jonah Rosenthal\n|| 26 April 2014 (USA) \n|| {{flag|Kenya}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Bridging Worlds: The Life and Teachings of Rav Azriel Chaim Goldfein''\n|| David Sassoon\n|| 15 June 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Cairo Time''\n|| Amir Ramses\n|| 22 January 2015 (Kuwait)\n|| {{flag|Egypt}}\n|| [[Comedy film|Comedy]]\n|-\n|''Calabash''\n|| Gerardo Chapa\n|| \n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Carpe Kilimanjaro: An Alzheimer's Project''\n|| Zach Jordan\n|| \n|| {{flag|Kenya}} <br> {{flag|Tanzania}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Casablanca Calling''\n|| Rosa Rogers\n|| September 2014 (USA)\n|| {{flag|Morocco}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" style=\"t