hy]]\n|-\n|''It Never Rained on Rhodes''\n|| Barry Salzman\n|| \n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''It's Not Over''\n|| Andrew Jenks\n|| 1 December 2014 (Belgium)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''I've Seen the Unicorn''\n|| Vincent Chung Toi Wong\n|| 25 April 2014 (Canada)\n|| {{flag|Mauritius}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''[[Iyore]]''\n|| [[Frank Rajah Arase]]\n|| \n|| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n|| [[Drama film|Drama]]\n|-\n|''Jenseits von schwarz und wei\u00df - Mission in Sambia;;\n|| Christoph Hertel\n|| 21 September 2014 (Germany)\n|| {{flag|Zambia}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Jesus was here''\n|| Mohammed Khairy\n|| \n|| {{flag|Egypt}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Jews of Egypt: The End of a Journey''\n|| Amir Ramses\n|| 3 June 2014 (Egypt)\n|| {{flag|Egypt}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Jikoo, a wish''\n|| Leroy Christophe\n|| \n|| {{flag|Senegal}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Joe''\n|| Erica Hill\n|| \n|| {{flag|Uganda}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''John of God the Movie''\n|| Sel\u00e9 M'Poko\n|| \n|| {{flag|Democratic Republic of Congo}}\n|| [[Comedy film|Comedy]]\n|-\n|''Journey of Rising Hopes''\n|| Brett Garling\n|| 20 April 2014 (Netherlands)\n|| {{flag|Tanzania}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Kalanda: The Knowledge of the Bush''\n|| Lorenzo Ferrarini\n|| \n|| {{flag|Burkina Faso}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Kalushi: The Story of Solomon Mahlangu''\n|| Mandla Dube\n|| 31 October 2014 (South Africa)\n|| {{flag|South Africa}}\n|| \n|-\n|''Kanyamakan''\n|| Said C. Naciri\n|| 12 March 2014 (Morocco)\n|| {{flag|Morocco}}\n|| [[Action film|Action]]\n|-\n|''Kawomera: Plant, Pray Partner for Peace with Subtitles''\n|| Marla Mossman\n|| TV Short May 2014\n|| {{flag|Uganda}}\n|| [[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''Kenya - Senior Project''\n|| Wesley McHaley\n|| \n||